  {
    "id": "f_csv_b37ac07387",
    "slug": "a-sentence-is-like-a-tune-a-memorable-sentence-gives-its-emotion-a-melodic-shap",
    "texto": "A sentence is like a tune. A memorable sentence gives its emotion a melodic shape. You want to hear it again, say it—in a way, to hum it to yourself. You desire, if only in the sound studio of your imagination, to repeat the physical experience of that sentence. That craving, emotional and intellectual but beginning in the body with a certain gesture of sound, is near the heart of poetry.",
